173778.en: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>Cooke, Cooke. This is a masterpiece.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173778.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「クッ……クックック。
　こいつぁ　傑作だ……。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173779.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>I heard that the only people who
gather in the Yang Clan are crooks who
distort the truth with light.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173779.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「陽衆に集まるのは　光で真実をゆがめる 
　ペテン師ばかりだってなぁ。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173780.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>You don't know. I've been around for
hundreds of years.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173780.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「アンタ　知らねえだろう。
　俺は　何百年も昔……<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173781.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>The Yang Clan is the result of the Yin
crowd being turned into human pillars.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173781.ja: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「陽衆の人柱にされた　陰衆の成れの果てだ。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173782.en:
I was put in harm's way and lost my life.The sword that sucked my blood at that time became a vengeful spirit of
hatred.
173782.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「俺は　危険な任にまわされ　命を落とした。 
　その時　俺の血を吸った刀に　
　憎悪の念が宿って　怨霊となった……。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173783.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>Those Yang Clan guys have always
forced their offshoots to do nothing
but dirty work.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173783.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「陽衆のヤツら　昔から　分家の陰衆には 
　よごれ仕事ばかり　押しつけやがって……。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173784.en: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>I hate it. Hateful.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173784.ja: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「憎い……。憎いねえ……。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173785.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>Hey, remember.The Yinshu are a family
that has been bullied by the Yang
Clan.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173785.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「なぁ　覚えておきなよ。 
　陰衆は陽衆によって　しいたげられた一族だと。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173786.en:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>The resentment is deep.It was further
deepened by the rites of heaven and
earth.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173786.ja:
<start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「その恨みは　深い……。 
　天地の儀によって　さらに深まった……。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173787.en: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>This grudge will never go away, Cooke.<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173787.ja: <start_lip_sync m13206 _normal m00001>「この恨みは　消えんよ……クックッ。<stop_lip_animation m13206 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173788.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001><pc>!Thought I'd come and
pick you up to see if you're almost
done.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173788.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「<pc>！ 
　そろそろ　終わるかなって思って
　迎えにきたよ。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173789.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Good job on your duties today! You did
a perfectly good job.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173789.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「今日も　お役目　お疲れさま！
　バッチリ　こなしてて　さすがだね。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173790.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>The Heaven and Earth Ceremony took
place here. I remembered it when I
came here.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173790.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「天地の儀は　この場所でおこなわれたんだ。
　……ここに来たら　思いだしちゃった。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173791.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>This is going to be a little long, but
I hope you'll listen.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173791.ja: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「少し長くなるけど　聞いてくれるかな。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173792.en:
The Tenochi no Rite is a ritual to summon the great phantom Tenotsu Kijin, who obliterated the Thousand
Night Storm a long time ago.
173792.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「天地の儀っていうのはね
　はるか昔　千夜嵐を消し去った　大幻魔
　テンオツキジンを召喚する　みわざのことだよ。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173793.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>There was a time when the druid was
not divided into yin and yang.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173793.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「かつて　天地雷鳴士が 
　陰と陽に　分かれてなかった時代……<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173794.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Our ancestors used to show their waza-
mae as druid in the presence of kings
with the rites of heaven and earth.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173794.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「あたしたちの先祖は　天地の儀をもって 
　天地雷鳴士としてのワザマエを
　王の御前で　示していたの。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173795.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>It was me and Yoi's fathers who
decided to revive it in this world.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173795.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「それを　今の世に復興しようと　決めたのは 
　あたしとヨイちゃんの　お父ちゃんたちだった。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173796.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Shinonome of the Yang Clan and Ouma of
the Yinshu are longtime rivals.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173796.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「陽衆のシノノメと　陰衆のオウマ……
　ふたりは　長年のライバル同士。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173797.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>They were also best friends who
dreamed of uniting the Yang Clan and
the Yin Shu.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173797.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「そして　陽衆と陰衆を　ひとつにしようと
　夢に見る　親友同士でもあった。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173798.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Yang Clan and Yinshu had a lot of
trouble in their history, but they
wanted a clean slate.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173798.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「陽衆と陰衆は　歴史の中で 
　たくさんのイザコザを　抱えちゃったけど
　それを　白紙に　戻そうとしたの。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173799.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>The reason why Yoi and I got along so
well was because of our fathers'
influence!<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173799.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「あたしと　ヨイちゃんの　仲がよかったのは 
　お父ちゃんたちの　影響だったんだ！<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173800.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Our father tried to bring the Yinshu
to the forefront of history.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173800.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「ウチのお父ちゃんは　陰衆を
　歴史の表舞台に　引きあげようとした……。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173801.en:
The Heaven and Earth Ceremony was the catalyst for this. And then, Yoi-chan and I, the next generation, were
chosen to be the central figures in the ceremony!
173801.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「天地の儀は　そのきっかけ。
　そして　次世代を担う　あたしとヨイちゃんが
　儀式の中心となる　神子に選ばれたのね！<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173802.en: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>But I failed.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173802.ja: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「だけど……あたしが　失敗した。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173803.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Tenotsu Kijin bit his precious spell
and was summoned as an evil spirit
with a raging soul.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173803.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「大切な呪文を……かんでしまって…… 
　テンオツキジンは　荒ぶる魂を宿した
　悪霊となって　召喚されたの。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173804.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>The evil spirit went on a rampage,
spreading mischief throughout
Kamiharmui Castle.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173804.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「悪霊は　大暴れして
　カミハルムイ城中に　災厄を振りまいた。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173805.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>My father and the others managed to
stop it and return the evil spirit to
the other world.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173805.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「お父ちゃんたちが　なんとか食い止めて 
　悪霊を　異界へ還してくれたんだけど……<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173806.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Yoi's father received a heavy Curse
for protecting me.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173806.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「ヨイちゃんのお父さんは
　あたしをかばって　重い呪詛を受けた……。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173807.en: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>And he died because of it.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173807.ja: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「そして　それがもとで……亡くなっちゃった。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173808.en: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>So I can't blame Yoi for hating me.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173808.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「だから　ヨイちゃんが
　あたしを恨むのは　仕方ないんだよね。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173809.en:
In addition, it was mistakenly thought that the Heaven and Earth Ceremony was a trap for the Yang Clan to entrap
Yinshu.
173809.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「おまけに……天地の儀は　陽衆が陰衆を 
　はめるための　罠だったんじゃないかって
　勘違いされちゃって。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173810.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Yinshu came to deeply, deeply resent
the Yang Clan.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173810.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「陰衆は　陽衆を　深く深く
　恨むようになったの……。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173811.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>I guess this is Asahi's youthful
mistake.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173811.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「これが　アサヒちゃんの　若かりし日の
　あやまちってヤツ……かな。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173812.en: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>But I'm not discouraged.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173812.ja: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「でも　あたし　めげないよ。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173813.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>I think I must be the one to carry on
the dream of uniting the Yang Clan and
the Yin people!<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173813.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「陽衆と陰衆をひとつにする　夢を継ぐのは
　あたしじゃなきゃって　思うの！<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173814.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>I couldn't talk to anyone for a long
time, so I feel a little better now
that you've listened.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173814.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「ずっと　誰にも話せなかったから
　聞いてもらえて　すこし楽になったよ。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173815.ja: <start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「……ありがとね。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173816.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Well then, let's go back to Yang Clan
Hideout. I have prepared a big thank-
you for you this time too.<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173816.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「それじゃあ　陽衆の隠れ家に帰ろっか。
　今回も　いっぱーい　お礼を用意したから。<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>

173817.en:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>Hey <pc>.Why can't we just
start over on our mistakes?<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
173817.ja:
<start_lip_sync n05098 _normal m00001>「ねえ　<pc>……。 
　どうして　失敗は　やり直せないんだろうね？<stop_lip_animation n05098 CLOSE_MOUTH>
